Title: Added Authenticator Based Two-Factor
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1693434612
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1

Checkmk now offers authenticator application based two-factor authentication (eg: Google Authenticator, etc). Navigating to <i>(User > Two-factor authentication)</i> will now present users with an option to register multiple time-based one-time password (TOTP) credentials.